2026-05-10T17:57:36.4226746Z 238        <!--
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4227115Z 239            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4227442Z 240            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4227763Z 241            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4228310Z 242            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4228530Z 243            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4228896Z 244            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4229356Z 245            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4229675Z 246            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-10T17:57:36.4230004Z 247            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
